title: Chrono Trigger Anime
description:
This is the hard to find (or at least it was for me) Chrono Trigger anime.  It was given out at some Japanese tradeshow after the game was released.  Quality isn't too good, but you can't really complain too much, its free.  Made by Akira Toriyama, character designer from the game and creator of Dragon Ball/Z


Enjoy and seed please, I have a bad connection and its hard to upload shit like this.
